Whether you are in the stands, on the field or out with friends, you'll be ready for game day with this Ladies' raglan athletic baseball tee. Specially designed with raglan sleeves and a shirt tail hem to give a sporty look with exceptional comfort.

Features:
4.5 oz. 100% combed ringspun cotton premium jersey

Flatlock stitched contrast ribbed collar and raglan armholes

Contrast double needle hem raglan 3/4 sleeves

Raw serge shirt tail bottom hem

Side seam construction for exceptional quality and durability
